.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-perform-mon-truc-en-plumes-at-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-3778447">Zizi Jeanmaire 的《Mon Truc en Plumes》</a> 。后来透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/why-lady-gagas-paris-olympics-2024-opening-performance-was-pre-recorded-3779667">她的表演是预先录制的</a>，30万名观众在屏幕上观看了表演，尽管对家里的观众来说是现场直播。 </p><figure id="attachment_3778701" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3778701" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3778701" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024.jpg" alt="嘎嘎小姐" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/lady-gaga-paris-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3778701" class="wp-caption-text"> Lady Gaga在巴黎奥运会开幕式上表演。图片来源：Sina Schuldt/图片联盟来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>奥运会编舞兼舞蹈主管莫德·勒普拉德克后来<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/global/lady-gaga-zizi-jeanmaire-performance-rain-olympics-choreographer-1236087753/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解释了为什么没有现场表演</a>，理由是当天的天气状况不佳。</p><p> “不幸的是，这是唯一一场[表演]，出于安全原因，我们必须在下午晚些时候预先录制，一旦我们确定要下雨——我们有每分钟的更新，我们有我们一生中从未如此仔细地关注过天气预报。”她回忆道。</p><p>另据报道，这位歌手留在现场观看了演出，她后来表示，她“只想创作一场温暖法国之心、庆祝法国艺术和音乐的表演”。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lady-gaga-and-bruno-mars-70s-country-themed-die-with-a-smile-music-video-3784255">观看 Lady Gaga 和 Bruno Mars 的 70 年代乡村主题“Die With A Smile”音乐视频</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
